[ti: I've Finally Arrived in Suzhou]
[length: 03:37.240]

[00:17.541]The train stops at Suzhou Station.
[00:21.013]The spring breeze brushes past me.
[00:25.321]I've been here thousands of times in my dreams.
[00:28.183]Today I can finally see it with my own eyes.

[00:32.720]The stone-paved road is still before me.
[00:36.316]The little bridge reflects the passing years.
[00:39.960]The scenes I once wrote about.
[00:43.631]All appear at this very moment.

[00:51.172]I've finally arrived in Suzhou.
[00:54.988]At the end of my dream.
[00:58.790]So after the evening breeze passes.
[01:02.138]There truly is the gentleness you described.

[01:24.664]Following the crossroads from old photographs.
[01:28.214]Walking to the other side of the story.
[01:32.520]Flowers bloom along the riverside behind me.
[01:35.692]Just like the tenderness you once described.

[01:40.138]The misty rain falls upon my shoulders.
[01:43.700]I walk through familiar street corners.
[01:47.576]I've been longing for so long.
[01:51.256]Just to arrive in this city.

[02:15.820]If time could turn back.
[02:19.419]I'd like to watch a rainstorm with you.
[02:23.162]Even if we were destined to miss each other.
[02:26.384]At least I've been here.

[02:34.863]I've finally arrived in Suzhou.
[02:38.181]At the end of my dream.
[02:42.028]When the flowers truly bloom.
[02:45.737]They're even gentler than I imagined.
[02:49.564]If one day you look back.
[02:53.168]You may still find me waiting here.
[02:56.905]This time not in a dream.
[03:00.577]But on the streets of Suzhou.

[03:08.023]The flowers in Suzhou have bloomed.
[03:12.025]So spring is still here.
[03:16.024]Everything you once told me.
[03:19.389]Was true.